description: This file defines interfaces for Logging object, providing APIs to get and set boolean parameters. It is part of the COSA Data Model Library for device management, specifically for logging configuration.

methods.name: Logging_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves the boolean value of a specified logging parameter.

methods.name: Logging_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets the boolean value of a specified logging parameter.
